      <p>Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) is the process of improving the visibility of your site in Google’s search results,
        essentially putting your business at the forefront of your target audience – an integral part of your digital marketing strategy. </p>
      <p>There are two main rules of thumb when following an SEO strategy:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>On-Page SEO</strong> This should be considered early on in the planning of your website design and
          development as you'll need to build and think about keywords in your headings, friendly URLs, site speed and
          metatags for example (don’t worry…we can go into more discussion about all of this).</li>
        <li><strong>Off-page SEO</strong> This focusses on factors outside of your website, and fundamentally draws on
          the relevance, trust and authority it has for your target audience/customers. Building backlinks from reputable
          sites is an area we’d focus on with you.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>With affordable prices specifically tailored to your needs, we will work with you on analysing your requirements
        and determining exactly what’s required.</p>
    </div>
